title: Squid Game Masked Soldier Vinyl Figure
body_html:
"I would like to extend a heartfelt welcome to you all." The Masked Soldier Makes their Youtooz debit with absolutely no sinister intentionsâ€¦ Standing at 4.5 inches tall, he holds a grey submachine gun at the ready in his gloved black hands as he wears a pink jumpsuit covered in utility pockets. The hood is raised over his head leaving only his black mesh mask revealed, its front has a 'T' plating at the bottom while the top is printed with a large white triangle. The exterior of his packaging sees him standing in front of a group of pink jumpsuits soldiers standing in formation on top of a set of stairs. The interior is a deep black and is laden with grey symbols which spill onto the protective packaging that has a pink bow running across it, all while his figure can be seen through the large clear window at its front.

  • Height 4.5"
  • This collectible ships in a matte, embossed, protective outer sleeve and a custom sized plastic protector for maximum protection during shipping.
